- Key storage constants: `factlockcam_app/lib/core/ghost_key/key_storage_keys.dart`
- Custody service: `factlockcam_app/lib/core/ghost_key/key_custody_service.dart`
- Keystore: `factlockcam_app/lib/core/ghost_key/factlock_keystore.dart`
- Router gate: `factlockcam_app/lib/app/router/app_router.dart`
- Burn UI: `factlockcam_app/lib/ui/mobile/settings/burn_account_view.dart`
- Restore UI: `factlockcam_app/lib/ui/mobile/settings/restore_archive_view.dart`
